video_title: ￼￼This is EXACTLY what it means to master your mind #anxiety #motivationalspeaker
transcript:
hey you need to hear this today nothing
in this world can bother you as much as
your own mind it may seem like other
people are pissing you off or bothering
you or making you sad or offending you
by what they say but it has nothing to
do with them it has everything to do
with your reaction to them it's all here
as Elanor Roosevelt once said no one can
make you feel inferior without your
consent so what you have to do is learn
how to master your mind
